# Kalyan Jewellers Billing System (Python)

## Description
This is a console-based Python mini project that simulates a jewellery billing system similar to Kalyan Jewellers.

The program calculates the total gold price based on weight and making charges. It also applies discounts based on gender, age, and purchase amount.

## Features
- Gold price calculation
- Making charges calculation
- Discount based on conditions
- Final payable amount display

## Concepts Used
- if / elif / else
- arithmetic operations
- user input
- variables


